$ Csound: tied notes

In order to create a tied note, the `p3` parameter of the → Kunst/Musik/Csound/Score-Statements#score-stmt-i[`i`] → Kunst/Musik/Csound/Score-Statements[score statement]
must be negative.
-
It then ties the note to the next note with the same instrument number. (Apparently, this is why there are fractional instrument numbers in → Kunst/Musik/Csound[Csound]).

{ Opcodes related to tied notes

  → Kunst/Musik/Csound/Opcodes/tival,
  → Kunst/Musik/Csound/Opcodes/tigoto,

}
